{"tid":1223004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"物資站其實有好大問題囉","createTime":"2019-06-14T15:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T15:15:35.000Z","uid":28068,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8cae2dd5caaa27593ff94d0b80c4d3bc858b4038","tid":1223004,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"隔離有個物資站post<br />\n見到真係嬲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本由頭到尾唔係物資站既問題<br />\n最大問題係你呢班參與既所謂義士又好示威者又好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都唔肯拎番屬於自己個份既物資<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個個黎到就放低一袋二袋 拍拍patpat就走人<br />\n你估你咁就幫到手？<br />\n你搞到人地物資站做到停唔到手咋!!!</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n物資站係咁要幫你地新送黎既物資分類<br />\n但你班人又唔拎番應有既物資<br />\n包括一人拎一兩個口罩，護目鏡，頭盔，一兩支哮喘藥，一兩支洗眼水，少量食物食水<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你就算當時用唔著，見到物資站有咁多剩餘物資好心就拎番一兩個走<br />\n之後就算唔係你用都可以幫手派俾人啦！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔該你班人做下好心   唔好再係度兩手fing fing<br />\n見到有多剩餘物資就拎黎用 或者幫手keep少量係自己個袋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你班友知唔知係物資站幫手每日要將d野搬黎搬去好L辛苦呀！！！<br />\n仲要搬黎唔知做乜9！！！搬完d野又係無人拎黎用！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"07afbfd70ae8e8cb99fdc1f9afa43ca25c4b6f60","tid":1223004,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2b0599ccbe3359f6ecac228136c90701719f19f9","tid":1223004,"uid":67151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:10:20